# 贡献代码

1. Fork
2. 创建分支 (`git checkout -b my-new-feature`)
3. 提交修改 (`git commit -am 'Added some feature'`)
4. 推送到远程仓库 (`git push origin my-new-feature`)
5. 然后到 github 网站的该 `git` 远程仓库的相应分支下发起 Pull Request
